---
title: Beef Rump & Creamy Peppercorn Sauce with Mash & Balsamic Veggies
description: You can't go wrong with mashed potato and beef steak, but you'll be making all the right moves when you add our creamy peppercorn sauce. Go one step further with a side of roasted balsamic veggies and you're set for success!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-rump-peppercorn-sauce-f425c9fe.jpg
